This project calculates the **Total Cost of Ownership (TCO)** for equipment across multiple years and includes a custom-built **service contract scheduling algorithm** that automatically assigns each product to service year categories (Y1, Y2, Y3â€¦) based on manufacturing and purchase timelines.

